; Tests for the quantity() function
; Extracts the numeric portion from an amount, stripping the commodity

2012-01-01 Test quantity function
    Assets:Test                       $100.00
    Equity:Opening

; Positive test: extract quantity from plain number
test eval "quantity(100)"
100
end test

; Positive test: extract quantity from another number
test eval "quantity(42.5)"
42.5
end test

